title: Amber Rose fires back at Tyga for dissing Blac Chyna over Ferrari (PHOTO)
content:
Amber Rose has fired back at Tyga who slammed Blac Chyna for not owning a Ferrari. It all started after Chyna threw shade at Tyga for allegedly leasing the Ferrari he gave Kylie Jenner. Tyga hit back at her with "where your ferrari though "?
Talk about friends sticking for each other..In other news, Amber's car is sick! Lovely colour.
source: All In One Place: Omoba's Blog
